file.name: httpbin.openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: httpbin
  description: API Management facade for a subset of an awesome httpbin.org API
  version: "1.0"
servers:
  - url: https://httpbin.org
paths:
  /status/{code}:
    get:
      description: Returns provided HTTP Status code
      operationId: status-get
      parameters:
        - name: code
          in: path
          description: Status code to return.
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            default: 200
            enum:
              - 200
      responses:
        default:
          description: Requested status code and empty body
    post:
      description: Returns provided HTTP Status code
      operationId: status-post
      parameters:
        - name: code
          in: path
          description: Status code to return.
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            default: 200
            enum:
              - 200
      responses:
        default:
          description: Requested status code and empty body
  /get:
    get:
      description: Returns GET data
      operationId: get
      responses:
        200:
          description: Request args, headers, origins, and url
          content:
            "application/json":
              schema:
                type: object
  /post:
    post:
      description: Returns POST data
      operationId: post
      responses:
        200:
          description: Request args, data, headers, origins, and url
          content:
            "application/json":
              schema:
                type: object
components: {}
